請假係咩一回事"},{"pid":"b478f4951e274cfc5fb3cc6d15e62cbb2e01c9eb","tid":296052,"uid":26852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:29:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女朋友已經on9<br />\n你都仲唔分手</blockquote><br />\n一齊左好多年 唔想因爲啲咁幼稚嘅事就分開<br />\n但唔明點解佢會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936d02bee2ebc7e5876e086f17870703a14c5769","tid":296052,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:29:58.000Z","msg":"港女 不要也罷"},{"pid":"04bdf3712d8ee2cf7cbbd01597ce9d6f38ed220c","tid":296052,"uid":63734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"都唔係幼稚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分明就弱撚智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔返工撚有錢慶祝咩"},{"pid":"9fea4bed9511b28e17d5658f1ae38eae50305e89","tid":296052,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:31:00.000Z","msg":"好唔好屌先，唔好屌就飛撚左佢啦"},{"pid":"369bb3e6e3084ee6f673028d65c62d9a342ec955","tid":296052,"uid":26852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港女 不要也罷</blockquote><br />\n返左4日工 日日都係咁嘅嘈<br />\n但我知佢係因為好緊張我<br />\n但只係真係好煩 好幼稚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c780944041df24b14b6670a58ecc130cd3d2ca","tid":296052,"uid":123511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"樓主同女朋友差幾多歲"},{"pid":"70e8ccb38ca7804b365499f6c8e7cbf46d263b72","tid":296052,"uid":26852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都唔係幼稚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分明就弱撚智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔返工撚有錢慶祝咩</blockquote><br />\n佢其實唔係真係想慶祝咩 <br />\n係想我可以好似讀書個陣咁 <br />\n日日陪住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n所以佢好唔鍾意我咁快返工<br />\n但現實冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699052cbb1a95e1e7b89d0f35a7c5295e207c910","tid":296052,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>港女 不要也罷</blockquote><br />\n返左4日工 日日都係咁嘅嘈<br />\n但我知佢係因為好緊張我<br />\n但只係真係好煩 好幼稚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲早比帽你帶,以前我女朋友仲讀緊U, 唔明返fulltime有幾多難處, 我好想多D時間同佢相處, 唔想佢用左D時間去返part time, 本身一星期可能都已經見到好少...<br />\n<br />\n當然,最後佢跟左佢男同學一齊"},{"pid":"b97e0b462bd0470ae83ffd780d066f0ce8a75377","tid":296052,"uid":26852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主同女朋友差幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n大家都係17FG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe74b22767567480bcb9001e9bf2038a510be59","tid":296052,"uid":18764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:43:51.000Z","msg":"你收工搵佢唔得咩？"},{"pid":"1c67be8df73d5f587b054b68dcca0699d9256439","tid":296052,"uid":123511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主同女朋友差幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n大家都係17FG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你叫佢試下番工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女人呢啲野 唔自己試過唔知究竟有幾撚煩"},{"pid":"a7eaded86f98b4e3f1